{
  "stem": "21437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think that my dad wanted to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as he had friends, I mean, business acquaintances not far from there where-- this is where the trees were brought in, close to the border there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I remember just that we were traveling with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandfather was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were traveling-- I don't know exactly how to describe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not a buggy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were two horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was like a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], it's called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You don't see it here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow, I was trying to think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was like a-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] it was something like a buggy, but it was made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was quite large.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you put, you know, bits and pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we fit it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember the planes flying over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember we were-- the bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember, we were sort of automatically, as we went along, we were sort of jumping into the ditches on this side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And somehow, mercifully, nothing happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were in one piece.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We heard all of those noises, the moaning, and groaning, and people being hit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I remember, I can see it when I talk about it, whatever I am telling you now, I can visualize it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the sounds escape me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Mercifully, the sounds escape me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I think the sounds were so horrendous, you know, that somehow I had to distance myself from something [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to visualize it, to see, actually.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was so terrible, really, to see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
